content.problem:
Find the surface area of a right triangular prism whose base is a 
right triangle with legs 6 cm and 8 cm, and whose height is 12 cm.

center
tikzpicture[scale=0.5]
 % Base triangle
 (0,0) – (6,0) – (0,4) – cycle;
 (0,0) rectangle (0.4,0.4);
 at (3,0) {6};
 at (0,2) {8};

 % Prism extension
 (0,0) – (2,2);
 (6,0) – (8,2);
 (0,4) – (2,6);
 (2,2) – (8,2) – (2,6) – cycle;
 (6,0) – (8,2) – (2,6);
 (0,0) – (2,2) – (2,6);

 at (8,3) {$h = 12$};
tikzpicture
